item.title: About
item.description: Wayne Lee Quick background: Dropped out of college to pursue professional gaming Started my infosec journey in BD/Sales Learned some Python around to automate work Decided to jump on HTB around July 2019 to learn how to hax stuff OSCP - Dec 2019 OSWE - May 2020 As a college dropout, I didn’t have a formal education in Computer Science but I did tinker a lot with the computer ever since I was a kid.
